Swarm kiting has injured us as a class.  It's so grossly overpowered that it has become the xp method of choice for a generation of one-trick-pony bards who cannot find their flutes with both hands.  It's made our class name synonymous with careless training and camp monopolizing.  To add insult to injury, it's done this to the class that was designed to be the most group-friendly, elegantly flexible class in the game.  <br>
